==Starting out==
===Inspecting Sir Amik Varze===
* '''Aris:''' To protect this noble knight from the magic of the culinaromancer, you will have to give him a creme brulee.
* '''Aris:''' Not just any creme brulee mind you, but a creme brulee supreme!
* '''Player:''' Well that doesn't sound too hard. What's so supreme about a creme brulee supreme?
* '''Aris:''' Are you going to constantly ask me questions?
* '''Aris:''' I am a fortune-teller, not a cook, and again I would suggest you speak to the cook next door who will be much more helpful on such culinary matters.
* '''Aris:''' Although I happen to know that one of the ingredients is the egg of the evil chicken.
* '''Player:''' The evil chicken? Great. He only ever seems to show up when I don't want him to.
* '''Aris:''' I believe the wise old man in Draynor has studied the Evil Chicken.
* '''Aris:''' I would suggest you speak to him to get you on the right track. And tell him Bubbykins says hi.
* '''Player:''' Er... Bubbykins?
* '''Aris:''' That is not important right now. Go! Protect Sir Amik from the magic that threatens his life, my spell will only hold so long!
* '''Player:''' Just give me 5 minutes and I'll be back!
* {{tact|end}}

